milestones.description: Brijesh Patel has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 180 runs, going past Gavaskar's 161
Ken Wadsworth has broken the record for most sixes (3) in ODIs for NZ, going past Peter Coman's 2
Glenn Turner has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs for NZ, going past Hadlee's 4
Bhagwath Chandrasekhar and Pochiah Krishnamurthy's 17-run partnership is IND's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 15 between Ashok Mankad and Madan Lal
Glenn Turner has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for NZ, going past Ken Wadsworth
Madan Lal has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for IND, going past Brijesh Patel
Pochiah Krishnamurthy has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (2) in ODIs for IND, going past Engineer's 1
